  "text": "Next to the new idea of bringing exposure into social capital research, an advantage of this study over the existing literature is its sophisticated measurement of neighbourhood social capital using an ecometric method [CITATION_1] instead of simple aggregation. Correlations of the two different methods for aggregating individual perception to the neighbourhood level were not extremely high (0.808), indicating the adequacy of the ecometric method.",
